text: Doug Clark is a former member of the Arizona House of Representatives from January 2007 until January 2009. He was elected to the House for his only term in November 2006, representing District 6. He did not run for re-election in 2008. ==References== Category:Arizona Republicans Category:Members of the Arizona House of Representatives Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Doug Clark (Arizona politician)
